Package src.interfaces

Interface AssaultPartyInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AssaultParty
    public interface AssaultPartyInterface
    Assault Party is constituted by Ordinary Thieves that are going to attack the museum. Assault Party is shared by the thieves
